<h2>How do I invest in cryptocurrency?</h2>
<p>Cryptocurrencies can be bought via brokers and via a cryptocurrency exchange - an online platform for buying, selling and trading crypto in a secure and efficient way. You can place an order on the exchange, specifying the amount and price at which you want to buy, your coin will then be credited to your exchange wallet which can then be transferred to your personal wallet. </p>
